name: Airy Downtown 1BR Near Harbor w/ Concierge
description:
The Devonshire features modern apartments in an historic neighborhood. A short walk in any direction will lead you to local history, like the Boston Tea Party Ships & Museum and the Paul Revere House. You're also within walking distance of the Rose Kennedy Greenway trails, Waterfront Park views, and shopping at Faneuil Hall. Additional neighborhood highlights include the Boston Public Market, Suffolk University, Massachusetts State House, and popular eateries like Union Oyster House, Yvonne's, and Central Wharf Co.

Enjoy a stay with Zeus! We have 2940+ reviews (see below).

The space
At Zeus, we offer thoughtfully furnished homes for 30+ day stays.
